text: February 14, 2018 / 10:23 PM / Updated 12 hours ago UPDATE 3-ATP World Tour 250, Memphis Men's Singles Results Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 15 (OPTA) - Results from the ATP World Tour 250, Memphis Men's Singles matches on Wednesday .. 1st Round ..
